modName: Rustic Elven Armor by Will Keith
descriptionHtml:
I didn\'t really like the golden color of the Elven armor, so after about 3 days of trying and failing to actually get this (Censored) replacer to work, I finally had success. I couldn\'t have done it without the help of David Brasher\'s retexturing tutorial, seen here- http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=740 -Thanks a crapton bro.

Installation: Extract it to your skyrim Data folder, normally seen here: C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\Data -Although yours could be different, you know that better than I do.
author: Will Keith
